{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lan_gong_yuan","speaker_name":"兰宫媛","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"上趟明明刺中你，为何竟丝毫没有事呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":268,"line_start":6,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lan_gong_yuan","text":"媛小姐为何听命于田单？是否因为齐雨的关系？","tone":"疑问","chapter":268,"line_start":10,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_lan_gong_yuan","speaker_name":"兰宫媛","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"媛媛身为齐人，自要为我大齐尽点心力。不过对上将军奴家却是非常仰慕的。","tone":"平静","chapter":268,"line_start":14,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua","speaker_name":"仲孙玄华","listener":"char_lan_gong_yuan","text":"媛媛今晚移情别恋，只顾与上将军说亲密话，是否该罚一杯？","tone":"调侃","chapter":268,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_lan_gong_yuan","speaker_name":"兰宫媛","listener":"char_jie_zi_yuan","text":"移情别恋的另有其人，罚的该是解大人而非妾身呢。","tone":"调侃","chapter":268,"line_start":22,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_jie_zi_yuan","speaker_name":"解子元","listener":"char_lan_gong_yuan","text":"该罚该罚。但媛媛也该罚，且须以曲代酒，哈！","tone":"大笑","chapter":268,"line_start":26,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_zhong_sun_long","speaker_name":"仲孙龙","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"二王子为何竟会迟来呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":268,"line_start":44,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_jie_zi_yuan","speaker_name":"解子元","listener":null,"text":"不若派人去催催看？","tone":"陈述","chapter":268,"line_start":48,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua","speaker_name":"仲孙玄华","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"听解大人说，柔师妹明天会来找上将军试剑。若上将军不介意，玄华可否忝陪末席，见识上将军的威风。","tone":"认真","chapter":268,"line_start":50,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua","text":"雕虫小技，怕不堪入玄华兄之目。","tone":"陈述","chapter":268,"line_start":56,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_zhong_sun_long","speaker_name":"仲孙龙","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"上将军太谦虚了！","tone":"大笑","chapter":268,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_lan_gong_yuan","speaker_name":"兰宫媛","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"上将军见过曹公吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":268,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_tian_bang","speaker_name":"田邦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"田邦闻得上将军大驾在此，特来一睹尊容，希望上将军莫要怪我等唐突。","tone":"平静","chapter":268,"line_start":78,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_qi_yu","speaker_name":"齐雨","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项兄别来无恙，闻说雅夫人客死咸阳，此事确令人遗憾。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":268,"line_start":82,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_ma_cheng_jia","speaker_name":"麻承甲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"在下麻承甲，一向对上将军的剑法极为神往，不知可否在上将军与曹公一战前，让在下先领教绝艺？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":268,"line_start":88,"line_end":90}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":["上将军","项兄"],"identity":"秦国上将军","faction":"秦国","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"穿越时空的战国英雄，百战宝刀之主","personality":{"traits":["勇猛善战","机智过人","重情重义","收敛锋芒","怜香惜玉","实战经验丰富"],"speech_style":"豪爽中带机敏","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":6,"line_end":8,"text":"兰宫媛问项少龙被刺中为何没事"}]},{"id":"char_zhong_sun_long","name":"仲孙龙","alias":[],"identity":"齐国贵族","faction":"齐国","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"齐国权贵，设宴款待项少龙","personality":{"traits":["圆滑世故","精于算计","善于应酬","重视利益","审时度势"],"speech_style":"客气恭敬","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":44,"line_end":46,"text":"仲孙龙举杯敬酒问二王子"}]},{"id":"char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua","name":"仲孙玄华","alias":[],"identity":"仲孙龙之子，曹秋道弟子","faction":"齐国","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"仲孙龙之子，剑术高超","personality":{"traits":["武艺高强","暗藏心机","表面恭敬","善于观察","不甘示弱"],"speech_style":"文武兼备","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":50,"line_end":54,"text":"仲孙玄华