{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ma_cheng_jia","speaker_name":"麻承甲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"既是如此，请上将军立即出剑，让我麻承甲领教高明吧！","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":268,"line_start":116,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_ma_cheng_jia","text":"既是相逼不已，那就动手吧！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":268,"line_start":120,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_ma_cheng_jia","text":"拔剑！","tone":"厉声","chapter":268,"line_start":142,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua","speaker_name":"仲孙玄华","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"难怪上将军名盖咸阳，连师尊都动了要和你比试的心，如此刀法，实世所罕见。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":268,"line_start":168,"line_end":170},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":null,"text":"二王子既然不来，我们不若早点回家睡觉！","tone":"微笑","chapter":268,"line_start":174,"line_end":176}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_tian_jian","name":"田建","alias":["二王子"],"identity":"齐国二王子","faction":"齐国","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"齐国二王子，势利观望","personality":{"traits":["势利眼","随风摆动","谨慎多疑","缺乏担当","善于观望"],"speech_style":"无直接对话","temperament":"犹豫"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":106,"line_end":108,"text":"齐雨说二王子不能抽空来"}]},{"id":"char_lv_bu_wei","name":"吕不韦","alias":[],"identity":"秦国权臣","faction":"秦国","role":"villain","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"秦国丞相，暗中与田单勾结","personality":{"traits":["老谋深算","野心勃勃","善于煽动","阴险狡诈","权倾朝野"],"speech_style":"无直接对话","temperament":"阴沉"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":110,"line_end":114,"text":"吕不韦和韩竭极力煽动田建"}]},{"id":"char_han_jie","name":"韩竭","alias":[],"identity":"吕不韦门客","faction":"秦国","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"吕不韦门客，曾追求凤菲","personality":{"traits":["善于花言巧语","表里不一","嫉妒心强","搬弄是非","薄情寡义"],"speech_style":"无直接对话","temperament":"阴沉"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":114,"line_end":114,"text":"韩竭自是大鼓如簧之舌"}]}],"skills":[{"id":"skill_bai_zhan_dao_fa","name":"百战刀法","type":"刀法","faction":"秦国","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"项少龙的百战宝刀刀法","techniques":[{"id":"tech_bai_zhan_bao_dao_dao_fa","name":"百战宝刀刀法","type":"attack","description":"以百战宝刀施展的刚猛刀法"},{"id":"tech_bai_zhan_pi_feng_shi","name":"百战劈风式","type":"attack","description":"百战刀法中的劈砍招式，以雷霆之势自上而下劈击，气势如虹"}],"progression":"大成","effects":["一刀断剑","气势震慑"],"combat_style":"刚猛霸道","rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":136,"line_end":156,"text":"项少龙一刀击败麻承甲"}]}],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":120,"line_end":122,"text":"项少龙怒从心起应战"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_tian_jian","type":"对手","intensity":40,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"势利观望令人心寒"},{"action":"add","target":"char_lv_bu_wei","type":"宿敌","intensity":90,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"暗中勾结田单"}]},{"id":"char_ma_cheng_jia","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":116,"line_end":118,"text":"麻承甲再次挑战"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"宿敌","intensity":80,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"挑衅被一刀击败"}]},{"id":"char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":168,"line_end":170,"text":"仲孙玄华赞叹项少龙刀法"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"由试探转为敬佩"}]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":286,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"韩竭来找过人家，说尽好话，奈何我已心灰意冷，怎都听不入耳。真是奇怪，以前我只要想起他，心里便甜丝丝的，现在只觉他空得个英俊的外表，为何我对他的看法会变化得这么大呢？","tone":"无奈","chapter":268,"line_start":180,"line_end":184},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"大小姐有什么打算？","tone":"疑问","chapter":268,"line_start":186,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"现在我只想静静地过一段风平浪静的日子，上将军可为我做出安排吗？","tone":"柔声","chapter":268,"line_start":190,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"只要应付过曹秋道，我立即带你返回咸阳，在那里有我保护你，还有什么好担心呢？","tone":"温柔","chapter":268,"line_start":194,"line_end":196},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我知你剑法高明，但在齐人心中，曹秋道已是天神而非凡人，为何你仍是成竹在胸的样子？曹秋道的剑从不留情，若你有什么三长两短，人家怎……怎……唉！凤菲不想活了。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":268,"line_start":198,"line_end":203},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"曹秋道仅是个凡人，只不过剑法比任何人都要厉害吧！我不是要硬充好汉的人，若没有保命的把握，今晚就和你溜了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":268,"line_start":206,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"莫要过于自信，齐人的形容或有夸大之处，但曹秋道横扫东南六国，却是不争事实。","tone":"担心","chapter":268,"line_start":212,"line_end":214},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"韩竭怕人家移情于你，说了你很多坏话，使我心中更鄙视他。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":268,"line_start":216,"line_end":218},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"谁可令全天下的人都欢喜呢？只好笑骂由人。咦！大小姐似乎对小弟这把刀很有兴趣哩！","tone":"调侃","chapter":268,"line_start":220,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"对你这把宝贝有兴趣的是曹秋道和齐国的剑手，我只对你的人有兴趣。斗争仇杀有什么乐趣？偏是你们这些男人乐此不疲，把我们弱质女流都牵累其中。韩竭临行前说你可能没命去见曹秋道，不过凤菲却没给他唬倒。","tone":"柔声","chapter":268,"line_start":226,"line_end":232},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"你听过麻承甲吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":268,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"不但听过，还在田单的相国府见过他，除仲孙玄华和旦楚外，论剑术，就要数他和闵延章。","tone":"陈述","chapter":268,"line_start":236,"line_end":238},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"为何提起他呢？这人相当可厌，态度嚣张，一副目中无人的样子，又以为自己很受女人欢迎，我只要看到他的模样便觉恶心。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":268,"line_start":240,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"原来你对男人的喜恶这么强烈。不过恐怕你有段时间会见不着他，他刚才寻上门来挑衅，给我一刀便在他额上留下永远磨灭不了的回忆。","tone":"得意","chapter":268,"line_start":244,"line_end":246},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"只是一刀？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":268,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"是小弟夸大了点，我还走了几步。","tone":"微笑","chapter":268,"line_start":250,"line_end":250},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"人家恨死你这得意洋洋的可憎样儿，你却偏是对人家不动心。","tone":"娇声","chapter":268,"line_start":252,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"我动心得要命，唉！谁能不对你动心？只是感情的担子太重，我家有三位贤妻，实在不敢再向别人用情。","tone":"无奈","chapter":268,"line_start":256,"line_end":260},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"人家早明白哩！雅夫人和倩公主对你造成很大的打击，是吗？","tone":"温柔","chapter":268,"line_start":262,"line_end":264},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"你怎会知道的？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":268,"line_start":266,"line_end":266},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"自然有人告诉我。","tone":"平静","chapter":268,"line_start":268,"line_end":268},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ping_er","speaker_name":"小屏儿","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"龙阳君求见上将军。","tone":"平静","chapter":268,"line_start":280,"line_end":280},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"无论是多么晚回来，记得来人家处。凤菲求的不是什么名分责任，只是一夕之缘吧！","tone":"温柔","chapter":268,"line_start":284,"line_end":286}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_feng_fei","name":"凤菲","alias":["大小姐"],"identity":"三大名姬之一","faction":"秦国","role":"companion","archetype":"healer","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"秦国三大名姬之一，对项少龙心生情愫","personality":{"traits":["多愁善感","敢爱敢恨","心灰意冷","柔情似水","洞察人心","果决干脆"],"speech_style":"柔媚中带真情","temperament":"多情"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":180,"line_end":184,"text":"凤菲对琴发呆诉说心事"}]},{"id":"char_long_yang_jun","name":"龙阳君","alias":[],"identity":"魏国权臣","faction":"魏国","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"魏国权臣，与项少龙有约","personality":{"traits":["深不可测","善于谋略","亦正亦邪","重情重义","行事诡异"],"speech_style":"无直接对话","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":280,"line_end":280,"text":"小屏儿通报龙阳君求见"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_ping_er","name":"小屏儿","alias":[],"identity":"凤菲侍女","faction":"秦国","role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"凤菲的贴身侍女","personality":{"traits":["忠心耿耿","乖巧伶俐","知礼守分","细心周到","低声细语"],"speech_style":"轻声细语","temperament":"平静"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":268,"line_start":280,"line_end":280,"text":"小屏儿的声音传上来"}]},{"id":"char_qing_xiu_fu_ren","name":"清秀夫人","alias":[],"identity":"齐国贵妇","faction":"齐国","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"向凤菲透露项少龙往事的神秘女子","personality":{"traits":["外表冷漠","内心热情","善于观察","守口如瓶","暗藏情意"],"speech_style":"无直接对话","temperament":"冷漠"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_ref